```python
class Parent1:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

class Parent2:
    def __init__(self, age):
        self.age = age

class Child(Parent1, Parent2):
    def __init__(self, name, age):
        Parent1.__init__(self, name)
        Parent2.__init__(self, age)
```

